room_title: Escape room "Shadow Detectives" by Crystal River Room Escape in Crystal River
room_address: 8740 Mayo Drive Suite #5 Crystal River, FL 34429
room_description:
The Underground Barber Society has hired Al Ketchum to locate Donald the Barber. Has it gone all wrong?
Your group has been contracted as SHADOW DETECTIVES to follow Mr. Ketchum and reveal the information he has uncovered about Donald.
You have 1 hour to find the clues and unravel the mystery before you are discovered!
